parameters:
\nc<Saki>Ugh, ugh... it hurts... every part of my body aches... and
it feels so heavy...

\nc<Saki>But I have to go to work... What time is it
now...?\bustMsgExp[1, 1]. . .
\nc<Saki>Eh!? 11 o'clock!? There are 52 missed calls from senpai!?
\nc<Senpai>Saki? Good, you answered the phone. Where are you right now?

\nc<Senpai>Overslept? I thought you might have just skipped out. I'm
not angry, so hurry up and come to work.

\nc<Saki>Um... I'm sorry, my body isn't listening to me... Every
joint is in so much pain... I can't muster any strength.

\nc<Senpai>I told you to take care of your health, didn't I? Your
condition is causing trouble for others.

\nc<Senpai>Enough. I'll let them know, so take the day off and make
sure you come in tomorrow.

\nc<Senpai>Just rest up for now. You'll be able to come in tomorrow,
right?

\nc<Saki>Whose fault do they think this is... Maybe I should really
just skip out. But then again, I have nowhere else to go...
\nc<Saki>Sigh... For now, I need to find some medicine.
